Method Detail

onNewSensorStatus

void onNewSensorStatus(int currentMessageCount,
                       int SensorLocation,
                       int BatteryStatus,
                       int SensorHealth,
                       int UseState)
Receives the data from a SensorStatus event.

Parameters:
currentMessageCount - The value of the message counter when this event was triggered. Useful for correlating multiple events. Rollover: the count is an integer incremented by one each message, rolling through the entire integer range.
SensorLocation - The AntPlusStrideSdmPcc.SensorLocationCodes of the current sensor location.
BatteryStatus - The P82_BatteryStatus.BatteryStatusCodes of the current sensor battery status. Note: This value may also be received in the AntPlusCommonPcc.IBatteryStatusReceiver.onNewBatteryStatus(int, long, BigDecimal, int, int) event if the sensor supports the battery status common page.
SensorHealth - The AntPlusStrideSdmPcc.SensorHealthCodes of the current sensor health.
UseState - The AntPlusStrideSdmPcc.SensorUseStateCodes of the current sensor use state.
